    public class Pac4jHTTPPostDecoder
extends org.opensaml.messaging.decoder.AbstractMessageDecoder<org.opensaml.saml.common.SAMLObject>
    Pac4j implementation extending directly the AbstractMessageDecoder as intermediate classes use the J2E HTTP request. It's mostly a copy/paste of the source code of these intermediate opensaml classes.
    Since:
    1.8
    Author:
    Misagh Moayyed
